<h1 align="center"><u>Soil Pollution: Definition, Causes, Effects and Solutions</u></h1><hr>
<p>Soil pollution is when the soil is contaminated by different pollutants like toxic chemicals from man-made products or even from wind or precipitation, which are natural pollutants. </p><hr>
